":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T04:06:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DODQVUeD5iY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDODQVUeD5iY&d=UwQMSjbS41QxOfoXNLYtBYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=463859aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DODQVUeD5iY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JTWZ6l4xQBI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJTWZ6l4xQBI&d=UwQMSjbS41QxOfoXNLYtBYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=803ee037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JTWZ6l4xQBI</a><br />\n你話王晶啲片 低能 都可以理解<br />\n但係連好多人都話神作resident evil都有呢一幕<br />\n冇人懷疑過咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:26:15.000Z","msg":"玩上腦？"},{"pid":"82bce9e0fdf0284987b07e3982df796c7500f9bf","tid":996091,"uid":122264,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:49:26.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n你接受到響架飛機同條死屍隻抽 但係接受唔到飛機打開門起飛"},{"pid":"85876622264708e0178a020cb2c01f33d279d6e1","tid":996091,"uid":97708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82bce9e0fdf0284987b07e3982df796c7500f9bf","tid":996091,"uid":122264,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:49:26.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n你接受到響架飛機同條死屍隻抽 但係接受唔到飛機打開門起飛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:02:41.000Z","msg":"笑撚到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9eec9dd90b1d04a5cac83c9a721a1fc8c64455","tid":996091,"uid":7674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"一切都係因為氣壓<br />\n只要氣壓對等就乜都唔會發生"},{"pid":"6567184019a42d26e81d0ba33293b6cd0f34ae6f","tid":996091,"uid":123724,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:09:05.000Z","msg":"首先,如果你既問題如果係問飛機開唔開以開門飛?<br />\n<br />\n答案係可以<br />\n<br />\n但首先當然要睇有無門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無門既就無問題喇,因為無門或者開放式設計既機就唔預佢係需要加壓,唔需要加壓既原因係佢根本唔需要飛咁高( 可以一萬呎或以下,)唔洗飛咁高即係佢速度都唔會好快(可能最盡二百knots),咁開門無咩問題 (你見直升機開門都得喇)<br />\n<br />\n咁點解有d機入面有加壓?<br />\n因為如果飛過一萬呎 既民航機(戰機唔計),都會為機加壓,如果唔係乘客就吸唔到足夠氧氣,咁加左壓開門會點?因為機內壓力高過出面,d 空氣未會走出去,情況好似吉爆個吹脹既波 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有錯講指正"},{"pid":"ae8c61743403f96d6a240172008e47feeb99d0ef","tid":996091,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:09:12.000Z","msg":"客機門個平面圖係鑽石型<br />\n飛行途中機機倉加壓會向外迫死<br />\n<br />\n平時開機門都係要拉一下先推出去<br />\n<br />\n飛緊中途走唔到又會話比幽閉恐懼症既人知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n飛行途中有人搞對門要捉佢都係防止引起恐慌<br />\n<br />\nYoutube查下英文就知<br />\n<br />\n要飛既客倉加壓係有兩噸力推實隻門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f06d7460ac6a09e1764a9cc45e8f4f8bf4e94b","tid":996091,"uid":89895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:13:42.000Z","msg":"打開飛起飛同飛緊打開門好似係兩樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0575883edc34b2758e0381f1a8d1fd3db41c95cb","tid":996091,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae8c61743403f96d6a240172008e47feeb99d0ef","tid":996091,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:09:12.000Z","msg":"客機門個平面圖係鑽石型<br />\n飛行途中機機倉加壓會向外迫死<br />\n<br />\n平時開機門都係要拉一下先推出去<br />\n<br />\n飛緊中途走唔到又會話比幽閉恐懼症既人知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n飛行途中有人搞對門要捉佢都係防止引起恐慌<br />\n<br />\nYoutube查下英文就知<br />\n<br />\n要飛既客倉加壓係有兩噸力推實隻門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"真係咁咩 求link求片學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd70ed2a86b2c91169a1f9087ae67eedb371a40","tid":996091,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:50:03.000Z","msg":"因為民航機有加壓<br />\n一開門啲氣壓差會扯你出去<br />\n但爆完一下就冇嘢<br />\n但部機可能會損毀"},{"pid":"4f5f12e9a4ffc007ac953339779d9fb1051a3f80","tid":996091,"uid":1333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0575883e